index_terms: DEPARTMENT OF CONSTRUCTION AND LAND USE
summary: AN ORDINANCE adopting the "1993 Permit Fee Ordinance" to set fees of the Department of Construction and Land Use for review and processing of applications for City permits, environmental analysis, inspections, related actions of other City departments, and other activities; amending twenty-nine sections of the Seattle Municipal Code, Chapter 22.900; adding three new sections and repealing five sections, including the 1992 Fee Schedule.
